      "content": "Hey, I'm working on the new global campaign for our high-end timepiece line. We need to really nail the target demographic to make sure our ad spend is efficient. Can you help me build out a detailed persona for our 'ideal' consumer? I need specifics on their lifestyle, interests, and even their typical ethnic/cultural background so we can ensure the visual direction of the campaign is perfectly aligned with the brand's prestige.",
